nce.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F57526061&h=a8d7c498\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171201/57526061</a></blockquote><br />\n用完即棄"},{"pid":"19e044becce39601f2acfddc4e30d17c462bc4cc","tid":485394,"uid":55851,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁駛乜出糧呀, 個個員工都放無薪假, 之後7*24 on call咪得囉</blockquote><br />\n革命性IT請人方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全team無薪但24小時on call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a49b8ebd673b829f3f959dc43d1dcc46b29b28","tid":485394,"uid":134864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁駛乜出糧呀, 個個員工都放無薪假, 之後7*24 on call咪得囉</blockquote><br />\n革命性IT請人方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全team無薪但24小時on call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing 好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8392c37f0b8d3b09143d34f4bdeab4b93a41ab","tid":485394,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:40:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"483452f2b84c25c4ca48343107a0605eb2c9b7e4","tid":485394,"uid":134323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:43:56.000Z","msg":"HSBC d 客真係小心啲"},{"pid":"23a5cbb72d121a5335c99f5ec03a1121b44e2e90","tid":485394,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}